table.description: This table holds alopecia scores on the colony
The table holds records of births for the colony
This table contains records of blood draws
This table holds body condition scores from the colony
This table contains cage observations, mapped to the animals present in the cage. It is separated from the cage_observations table in order to speed queries
This table contains records of clinical encounters for animals in the colony. Each encounter is equivalent to one visit, such as an exam, surgery or procedure.
Contains records of observations made on the animals in this colony
This table containers clinical remarks about the animals in the colony, primarily in the form of SOAP notes
This table contains records of dental assessments
This table contains records of drugs, medications and treatments given to the colony
This table contains final summary reports created to summarize procedures, surgeries and other exams
This table contains records of daily observations from the colony, entered by animal technicians
This table contains records of SNOMED codes associated with procedures
This table contains the problem list, which is similar to open cases, for each animal in the colony
This table contains records of TB tests
This table contains records of tooth assessments
This table contains treatments ordered for animals
This table contains records of weights
This table contains vitals recorded on colony animals, such as body temperature and heart rate
This table contains bacteriology test results
This table contains the results of chemistry tests
This table contains one row for each clinpath test that has been ordered. Results are stored in separate tables.
This table contains records of hematology morphology analyses
This table contains results of hematology tests
This table contains results of immunology tests
This table contains results of parasitology tests
This table contains results of urinalysis tests
This table contains results of virology tests
This table contains records of arrivals at the center
This table contains records of animal assignments
This table contains records of behavior observations, in the form of SOAP notes
This table contains records of charges
This table contains records of deaths
This table contains demographics data for animals in the colony
This table contains records of departures from the center
This table contains records of housing and housing transfers
This table contains inbreeding coefficients calculated on colony animals
This table contains records of menses observations
This table contains misc notes about colony animals
This table contains records of pregnancies
This table contains records of biopsies
This table contains morphologic diagnoses recorded after biopsies and necropsies
This table contains records of slides
This table contains records of necropsies performed at the center
This table contains records of organ weights
This table contains requests for tissues and other samples
This table contains records of tissue samples that have been collected
This table contains records of animal assignment to pools
